  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a requirement to activate this jutsu, you must have a weapon from the Polearm weapon group equipped.</p><p>This weapon gains +1 rank of the reach property.</p><p>All Bukijutsu you cast, that requires an attack roll or forces another creature to make a saving throw, that deals damage, gain pierce (5) for the duration.</p><p>Additionally, when you score a critical hit using your weapon with a weapon or Taijutsu attack, the target falls prone and reduces their movement speed by 15ft until the end of their next turn.</p>",
